# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .DX FOLDER STRUCTURE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# All cache and tool-specific files are stored in .dx folder:
#
# .dx/
# ├── cache/           # Global cache for all dx tools
# ├── forge/           # Build orchestration state
# ├── style/           # Compiled CSS cache
# ├── icon/            # Optimized icons cache
# ├── media/           # Processed media cache
# ├── font/            # Subsetted fonts cache
# ├── stack/           # Runtime/bundler cache
# ├── workspace/       # Monorepo dependency graph
# ├── generator/       # Generated code cache
# ├── driven/          # AI task state
# ├── unsafe/          # npm packages (untrusted)
# ├── serializer/      # Parsed config cache
# └── www/             # HTIP template cache
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
